   "source": [
    "## Resume after kernel restart\n",
    "\n",
    "If you hit OOM and restarted the kernel, run THIS cell instead of redoing Phase 1.\n",
    "It re-uses `V_refusal.pt` and `guardrail_heads.pt` from disk.\n",
    "Skip this cell on a fresh run that already executed Phase 1 in-process."
   ]
  },
